        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-15 21:55:02.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nEric, Currently this jobs is failing since it seems that the latest development in this project is happening on a released artifact:\nhttps://github.com/onap/externalapi-nbi/blob/master/pom.xml#L16\n\nDevelopment must happen on snapshot images and we should let the maven-stage job pick the pom.xml and produce a release artifact every day. \n\nIn general, the gerrit-maven-stage job is promoting an ideal maven workflow for development where the teams need to work on top of snapshots. \n\nOnce this version is changed to a snapshot one, the maven-stage job should work.\n\nLet me know if you have any questions",
        "patchset_number": 5
      },
